             was indicted <rs id="t18000917-69-off374" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000917-69-off374" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000917-69-off374" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               for feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000917-69-cd375" type="crimeDate">13th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-69-off374 t18000917-69-cd375"></join>, a saddle, value 10s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000917-69-victim741" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Carr
                        <interp inst="t18000917-69-victim741" type="surname" value="Carr"></interp>
